data.description: Desirable Plum Canyon, Fabulous Home, Paid SOLAR, Light And Bright With An Amazing Sunset View. Three bedrooms, a LARGE LOFT and 3 bathrooms. Enter into a wonderful open concept main floor. Living area, dining and kitchen are all open to each other, perfect for family gatherings. Kitchen is dressed in stainless appliances with a bar area, expansive countertop and huge walk in pantry. Large dining area can accommodate a family table, in addition, the living area is invitingly dressed in large windows and recessed lighting. Sliding door opens to the backyard, where you can soak in the outdoor spa and take in the gorgeous sunset. Nice grassy area for games and play. As you continue upstairs, the loft will beckon you as a place to relax, to game or even a home office area. The primary bedroom boasts a lot of space, a walk in closet and plentiful windows to enjoy the view. Primary bathroom is also spacious with a separate shower, tub and toilet room. Two additional bedrooms share the hallway bathroom. Laundry room is conveniently located upstairs, oversized for ample storage. Two car garage.*** Bonuses include: fully paid solar, newer wood laminate flooring downstairs, outdoor spa. This community offers VERY LOW HOA. Close to shopping and restaurants. MAKE SURE TO INQUIRE ABOUT ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE LOAN.
